# Sounds

This folder will contain audio files for the Kooka app.

## Planned Audio Assets

- Background music tracks
- Button press sound effects
- AR interaction sounds
- Success/completion sounds
- Ambient sounds for different AR themes

## File Formats

- MP3 files for music and long sounds
- WAV files for short sound effects
- OGG files for cross-platform compatibility

## Audio Guidelines

- Child-friendly and pleasant sounds
- Appropriate volume levels
- High quality but optimized file sizes
- Loopable background tracks
- Short and snappy sound effects
